# Financial Risk.Credit Credit Exposures Non Accrual With Provisions Impairment Amount

## identifier
de7847

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of the provision for impairment in relation to all exposures of the reporting party that give rise to counterparty credit risk, determined in accordance with the relevant prudential standards, where the estimates of future interest income are zero.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.Credit.CreditExposuresNonAccrualWithProvisionsImpairment.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
